## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src)=>{
  return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
    const image = new Image();
    image.loading = (e) => {
      resolve(image)
     }
    image.onerror = () => {
      reject(new Error('找不到该图片' + 'src'))
     }
    image.src = src
  })
}
